sentence: In early trading on Tuesday, shares of Walmart topped the list of the day's best performing Dow Jones Industrial Average components, trading up 2.0%.
Year to date, Walmart registers a 9.6% gain.
And the worst performing Dow component thus far on the day is Walt Disney, trading down 2.4%.
Walt Disney is lower by about 21.1% looking at the year to date performance.
Two other components making moves today are Home Depot, trading down 2.1%, and Intel trading up 1.1% on the day.
